Meet the new Ultimate Guitar!

We've been working hard together with users to create an all-new version of the UG flagship app.

1. One app for all platforms. 
Enjoy the same experience on every platform (WEB, iOS, Android). 

2. Tab page customization. 
Set the most suitable font style and size for the tab and use dark mode for a gig. 

3. Official Tabs.
Learn 7,000+ HQ tabs with backing tracks and synced lyrics made by professional guitarists. 

4. A new Listen feature. 
Watch videos to refresh songs in your memory or use it as a backing track. 

5. Sleek design. 
Cool, modern and practical.

If you have any questions - contact us at support.ios@ultimate-guitar.com, and we'll do our best to help you.

Keep on rockin'
